  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2025-03-05",
    "date": "2025-06-30T19:44:12Z",
    "text": "Hershel \"Woody\" Williams National Medal of Honor Monument Location Act\n\nThis bill requires the authorized monument\u00a0honoring Medal of Honor recipients to be located within the Reserve (the great cross-axis of the National Mall, which generally extends from the Capitol to the Lincoln Memorial and from the White House to the Jefferson Memorial)."
  },
